Posts.Content: Hello! I was called back for the same reason, I have dense breasts. They had me go back for an ultrasound. I was also so nervous and it ended up being nothing. They may just want to be thorough. I have a friend who went all the way to biopsy and it was nothing. Its better to be thorough. Breath and try not to stress too much. I know its easier said than done but one day at a time
Posts.Title: Dense Breast
